OL,3,CHope for child contact centre
OL,4,Cfollowing government u-turn
OL,6,FOn Saturday (8 February), Deputy
OL,7,FMalcom Ferey announced the government
OL,8,Fhad now secured adequate funding to
OL,9,Fensure Centrepoint's continued
OL,10,Foperations for the next two years.
OL,12,FThe Assistant Chief Minister says the
OL,13,Fgovernment has agreed funding for 2025
OL,14,Fand made a commitment for 2026.
OL,16,FHe says: "Providing ongoing dialogue
OL,17,Ffor children and families at what can
OL,18,Fbe very challenging times in their
OL,19,Flives is so valuable in producing
OL,20,Fbetter outcomes for our young people."
